text.textblock: Notice is hereby given that the following have been issued a Certificate of Financial Responsibility to Meet Liability Incurred for Death or Injury to Passengers or Other Persons on Voyages pursuant to the provisions of section 2, Public Law 89-777 (46 U.S.C. 817(d)) and the Federal Maritime Commission's implementing regulations at 46 CFR part 540, as amended:
Commodore Cruise Line, Inc., Commodore Shipholding Corp. I, Inc. and Effjohn International Cruise Holding Inc., 800 Douglas Road, Coral Gables, Florida 33134
